## 🔎 Reflection
This lab helped me understand how to launch and manage virtual servers in AWS.  
I learned how instance types affect cost and performance, how security groups act like firewalls, and how user data scripts can automate server setup.  
Resizing the instance and testing protections showed me how AWS makes scaling and safeguarding easy.  
